    dc:description "FIGURES 1–6. Oneilliella chicoi sp. n. (1) holotype female; (2) antenna; (3) head and pronotum; (4) fore wing; (5) meso- and metanotum and abdominal tergite I; (6) abdominal tergites II–VIII." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8281692/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8281696>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–15. Oneilliella funebris comb. n. (7) holotype female; (8) paratype male; (9) antenna (segments III–VIII); (10) fore wing; (11) head and pronotum; (12) meso- and metanotum; (13) meso- and metafurca; (14) abdominal tergites II–VIII; (15) male sternites V–VII." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8281696/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8281700>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16–23. Oneilliella tica sp.n. (16)holotype female; (17)antenna; (18) forewing; (19)head, pronotumand mesonotum; (20) meso- and metanotum and abdominal tergite I; (21) pro-, meso- and metasternum; (22) abdominal tergites I–VIII; (23) abdominal tergites IX–X." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8281700/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8281704>
    dc:description "FIGURES 24–30. Oneilliella wanessae sp. n. (24) female; (25) male; (26) antenna; (27) fore wing; (28) head and thorax; (29) abdominal tergites II–VII; (30) male abdominal sternites V–VII." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8281704/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8281706>
    dc:description "FIGURES 31–38. Oneilliella williamsi. (31) holotype female; (32) male; (33) antenna; (34) fore wing; (35) head, thorax and abdominal tergite I; (36) abdominal tergites III–X; (37) male abdominal tergites IX–X; (38) male abdominal sternites III–VII." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8281706/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

